Jack Kornfield,
what a pleasure it

00:22:49.680 --> 00:22:52.990 align:middle line:84%
is sharing these aspects
of the path with you.

00:22:52.990 --> 00:22:54.512 align:middle line:84%
Thanks so much
for being with me.

00:22:54.512 --> 00:22:56.470 align:middle line:84%
>> It's been a pleasure
for me, too, thank you.

